## 3. Advanced Interaction Patterns ðŸ”„ðŸ‘†

### 3.1 Concept Ghost Mode ðŸ‘»ðŸ”

Overlay visualization showing concept relationships while editing code:

```
â”Œâ”€ Regular Code Editor with Ghost Overlay â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”
â”‚ def process_payment(payment_data):                â”‚
â”‚     # Ghost overlay showing:                       â”‚
